1635
01:40:40,180 --> 01:40:43,040
 Mi možemo vježbati kroz svakodnevne pokrete.

1636
01:40:43,040 --> 01:40:45,200
 Dakle, penjenje na stepenicu,

1637
01:40:45,200 --> 01:40:47,840
 ako znaš aktivirati mišić gluteusa

1638
01:40:47,840 --> 01:40:52,640
 i napravit kontrolu mišića kora,

1639
01:40:52,640 --> 01:40:55,520
