01:42:44,080 --> 01:42:45,940
 Ne možemo mi,

1685
01:42:45,940 --> 01:42:49,540
 ako neko ima visoko stresan posao,

1686
01:42:49,540 --> 01:42:54,540
 ima poziciju u tom hjerarhijskom sudoku,

1687
01:42:55,120 --> 01:42:57,620
 sustavu u nekoj organizaciji,

1688
01:42:57,620 --> 01:43:01,540
